35:08.560 --> 35:16.280
fiction, there was never a new wave in the same sense. There were a lot of
waves. There were a lot of different people doing a lot of different things. The

35:16.280 --> 35:24.020
people that were identified as new wave were very diverse. I mean, what I was
actually writing was very different to say what Tom Dish was writing, or

35:24.020 --> 35:35.180
Boulard, or Zelazny, Delaney, who were also identified as new wave writers. this
